channel.title: cuber - oatmeal craisin cookies [lo-fi hip hop]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/averageteencuber/oatmeal-craisin-cookies
I made this track over the course of one afternoon, after my mom had made some cookies earlier that day; in the few weeks since then I've just done minor touch-ups and sat on it because I was too lazy to get the art set up. anyway, the main point of posting this was just to show I haven't stopped producing.
